Package: loadmeter
Source: loadmeter (1.20-6)
Version: 1.20-6+b2
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Uwe Hermann <uwe@debian.org>
Installed-Size: 59
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.7), libx11-6
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: http://www.zip.com.au/~bb/linuxreal/
Description: Attractive X11 load meter
 Loadmeter is an attractive X11 based system monitor. It displays
 load average, uptime, disk and memory usages. It uses a coloured
 bar graph display for easy reading and popup menus for other info.
 It uses less memory than xload.
